  "description_long": "Credit Advisors Council - Credit Repair Houston is a credit repair provider serving clients in Houston, Texas. The company serves consumers in the Houston area who are looking to repair and improve their credit scores.\n\nOperating as a financial consultant, Credit Advisors Council - Credit Repair Houston provides a range of services for consumers seeking credit repair solutions.\n\nWhen evaluating credit repair services in Houston, consumers should look for providers that dispute directly with all three credit bureaus \u2014 Equifax, Experian, and TransUnion. Key differentiators include transparency around pricing, realistic timelines for results, and whether the company offers a money-back guarantee. Credit Advisors Council - Credit Repair Houston operates in a highly regulated industry under the Credit Repair Organizations Act (CROA), which requires written contracts, a three-day cancellation window, and prohibits upfront fees before services are rendered.\n\nConsumers in the Houston, Texas area who are considering Credit Advisors Council - Credit Repair Houston should contact the company directly to discuss their specific situation and get current pricing information. As with any credit repair provider, it is advisable to compare multiple options, verify licensing and credentials, and read recent customer reviews before making a decision.",
